{"id": "art-153", "label": "Art. 153", "title": "Art. 153", "slug": "art-153", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 153 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1041972264\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2148\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1041972264\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Prin actul constitutiv se poate stipula c&#259;\nsocietatea pe <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> este administrat&#259; de\nun directorat <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> de un consiliu de supraveghere,\nîn conformitate cu prevederile prezentei <span class=SpellE>subsec&#355;iuni</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1965060701\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2147\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1965060701\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Actul constitutiv poate fi modificat în cursul <span\nclass=SpellE>existen&#355;ei</span> <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nprin hot&#259;râre a adun&#259;rii generale extraordinare a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>,\nîn vederea introducerii sau a elimin&#259;rii unei astfel de prevederi.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_42479747\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2146\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_42479747\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Prevederile prezentei <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:\nnormal'>legi</i> privitoare la cenzori nu sunt aplicabile <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\ncare opteaz&#259; pentru sistemul dualist de administrare.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><span style='mso-no-proof:\nyes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape id=\"Imagine_x0020_378778457\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2145\"\n type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;\n mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_378778457\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>PARTEA\nA:Directoratul</span></b></p>"}